column3: Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/637164b136fa324d0dc618e96a0091a979ceec02 for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/cu

Please fix this on transifex: https://www.transifex.com/projects/p/bitcoin/

Translations are pulled into this repository before releases.
